thread.title: Vote for the best place to eat in Cobb County

author: Kyle Nazario
title: Vote for the best place to eat in Cobb County
text:
Metro Atlanta's northwest county is full of great places to eat, but only one can be the best. Instead of us telling you which is No. 1, we're letting the readers decide. Take a look at the list below and vote up or down for which place in Cobb has the best grub.
We’ve also linked to the great work done by our food team in a couple places below. If you’re interested in reading more about a restaurant, click the link below the picture.
RECOMMENDED VIDEO: Spring Dining Guide: the best of brunch
2016 Spring Dining Guide: the best of brunch. Visit myAJC.com/dining to see the entire spring dining guide, which includes brunch: reviews, playlists, videos, blogs, quizzes, interactive maps and checklists. (Erica A. Hernandez/AJC)
